source.name: www.FuelEconomy.gov
source.description: FuelEconomy.gov provides comprehensive information about vehicles' fuel economy. The official U.S. government site for fuel economy information, it is operated by the Department of Energy and the Environmental Protection Agency. The site provides access to general information, widgets to help car buyers, and fuel economy datasets.
